  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Post is in the vibrant centre of the village, the beautiful St Nicholas’ church and <a data-udi="umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a5143c480274e36b9af49fb9e370cf0}" title="Westendorf">Westendorf</a> square are just outside the hotel. Skiers and snowboarders can get to the nursery slopes and ski school in less than five minutes. More experienced skiers can use the chairlift on the nursery slope to access the main village gondola. The Hotel Post team work hard to make everyone feel at home here, it has been in the same family for generations and still retains its original charm.</p>
<h2>Alpine style</h2>
<p>At Hotel Post you’ll notice traditional features in the original wing and a modern style of the newer wing, each area of the hotel has been carefully designed to make you feel at home. The cosy bedrooms are perfect for rest and relaxation, reflecting the beauty and charm of the Tyrolean Alps - each of the bedrooms is decorated in a typical alpine style with warm wood, equipped with everything you might need for a comfortable week in Austria.</p>
<p>The beautiful spa with sauna, steam room, whirlpool, infrared cabins and relaxation room is located in the new wing, it is perfect for relaxing after a hard day’s skiing. </p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>The hotel has a lively bar – you're just as likely to find yourself sitting next to one of the locals as a visiting skier. There is a dining room for guests on half-board and a-la-carte restaurant serving International and Austrian dishes in the cosy stube at the front of the hotel (Inghams guests choosing to eat at the a-la-carte restaurant receive a voucher in part-payment for their meal).</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Post the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
